            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1627383727984-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> with your<strong> ground turmeric</strong> in a small bowl with a small splash of <strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>turmeric yoghurt</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
